{"id":18495,"date":"2014-03-13T21:30:32","date_gmt":"2014-03-13T17:30:32","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/www.dailyhadithonline.com\/?p=18495"},"modified":"2024-07-24T16:39:57","modified_gmt":"2024-07-24T12:39:57","slug":"lineage-prophet-disown-child","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/03\/13\/lineage-prophet-disown-child\/","title":{"rendered":"Hadith on Lineage: The Prophet does not let him disown his child"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>Abu Huraira reported: A bedouin came to the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, and he said, \u201cIndeed, my wife has given birth to a black boy and I have disowned him.\u201d The Prophet said, \u201c<b>Do you have camels<\/b>?\u201d He said yes. The Prophet said, \u201c<b>What color are they<\/b>?\u201d He said, \u201cThey are red.\u201d The Prophet said, \u201c<b>Are any of them gray<\/b>?\u201d He said, \u201cThere are gray camels among them.\u201d The Prophet said, \u201c<b>Where do you think this color came from<\/b>?\u201d He said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, it is hereditary.\u201d The Prophet said, \u201c<b>Perhaps this boy\u2019s color is hereditary<\/b>.\u201d The Prophet did not allow him to disown his child.<\/p>\n<p>Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 7314, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 1500<\/p>\n<p>Grade: <b><i>Muttafaqun Alayhi<\/i><\/b> (authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and Muslim<\/p>\n<p align=\"right\">\u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0647\u064f\u0631\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0623\u064e\u0646\u0651\u064e \u0623\u064e\u0639\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0627\u0628\u0650\u064a\u0651\u064b\u0627 \u0623\u064e\u062a\u064e\u0649 \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u06